    <criterion testable="true">Dashboard placement decision (Bicep IaC vs portal-managed) is recorded in `notes/task-042-dashboards-evidence.md` with explicit rationale. If Bicep, the module follows the existing `infrastructure/bicep/modules/dashboard.bicep` precedent. If portal-managed, a reproducible JSON export exists at `infrastructure/dashboards/r5-summarize-dashboard.json` with adjacent re-import README.</criterion>
